questionnaire.question: PICOS POI # 1:  Do we have a Coke branded cooler in the Impulse Zone?   (The Impulse Zone is within 12 ft. of the register.  Electric Barrel coolers are acceptable. Ice Barrels do NOT count for Impulse Zone but do count for innovation brands in POI # 11. Must be incremental cooler placement, Cold Vault or Cold vault extension does not count.  )

1b.  Are all the 20oz SSD core brands plus Dasani 20oz represented in the Impulse Zone cooler?  (Core brands are Coke, Coke Zero Sugar, Diet Coke, Sprite, Dr Pepper [where distributed] and Dasani 20oz. )
PICOS POI # 2:  Is there a Sparkling can display?

2a. Are all core brands on display? (SSD core brands must be present.  Coke, Coke Zero Sugar, Diet Coke, Sprite and Dr Pepper (where distributed).  Any multipack SSD FC can product configuration is acceptable.  )
2b.  Is Dasani 12pk 12oz on display?
PICOS POI # 3:  Is there a Powerade Display in this outlet (any pkg)?

PICOS POI # 4:  Is there an incremental Branded (Monster, NOS or Full Throttle graphics) Energy Cooler in this outlet? (Incremental to the impulse zone cooler, Monster JAVA coolers do not count.  Monster JAVA coolers count in the Coffee POI # 8.)

PICOS POI # 5:  Is there a Sparkling PET display? (SSD core brands must be present [Coke, Coke Zero Sugar, Diet Coke, Sprite and Dr Pepper (where distributed)].  Any PET SSD FC PET product configuration is acceptable.  2 Liter, 1.25 Liter  count.  )
5a. Are all core brands on display?

PICOS POI #6: Is there a Still Display excluding Dasani Casepack Water in this outlet? (Display types could be an end cap, stand alone/free standing, rack or wing.  If displayed with other categories, it would still count toward this question. Incremental to 12pk 12oz Dasani on SSD Display.  Categories could include Energy, Tea, Sports, Water (excluding case pack water), TEY.)
PICOS POI # 7:  Is there an incremental SmartWater Display or Rack in this outlet? (Must be incremental to Still Display #1.)
PICOS POI # 8:  Is there a Branded Coffee Cooler in this outlet ? (Options include :  Dunkin Donuts, Monster Java, McCafe.  "Breakfast Center" Branding counts.)

PICOS POI # 9:  Do we have a Coke branded barrel, ice chest or incremental Coke identified cooler (cold availability) in the outlet? (Barrel and / or incremental cooler can have any branded SSD or Still logo.  Barrel and / or cooler must be incremental to Impulse Zone cooler.  Incremental cooler cannot be an extension of the cold vault.)
PICOS POI # 10:  Is there a Coke Identified Fountain in this outlet with pricing POS available (never on logo panel)?
PICOS POI # 11:  Is Gold Peak brewed tea, brewed coffee or tea tower available in this outlet?
12. Are there any Out of Stock Products in the Outlet? (Base OOS determination on POG and/or shelf tags. One SKU of any package or brand would result in an OOS.)
13: Is there a Premium SSD package offered cold in the outlet (8oz, 12oz glass, 8.5 oz aluminum or Import glass)? (Package must be cold not ambient)
14: Are there 5 flavors of Gold Peak 18.5oz "cold" available in this outlet?
15: Are there 5 flavors of Fanta 20oz "cold" available in this outlet?
16: Are there 2+ packages of SmartWater available in this outlet? (Includes cold vault and stand alone displays.)
17: Are there 2+ packages of Dasani available in this outlet? (Includes cold vault and stand alone displays.)
18:  Is Sparkling Can display in best position?
19:  Is Sparkling PET display in best position?
20: Is Still Display (excluding Dasani Casepack Water) in best position?

21: PICOS POI -  Is the KO SSD messaging "Taste the Feeling" for sparkling IC core brand package visible from the outside?  SSD IC Pkg./Price will vary. 
 (Messaging may be at curb, pump, or perimeter of store.  Examples include pole signs, bumper shrouds, pump blades, or window posters. )

22: Are there a minimum 5 SSD POI from curb to cold vault?   ("Taste the Feeling" for sparkling IC core brand package) (YES If there are five or more SSD points of contact. Banners/Coroplast-1, Pump Toppers/Gas Pump Signage-1, Push/Pulls/Window Signs-1, POS on a display-1, KO logo Fountain, Cold vault-1, Incremental KO branded cold equipment > POINTS ARE TO BE AWARDED BASED ON ZONE ACTIVATION LISTED ABOVE.)

23: PICOS POI -  Is there a Food Solution with SSD in this outlet?  
 (The meal or salty snack food bundle can be executed in any part of the outlet.  Sugar snacks should NOT be included (i.e. candy bars).  Combo pricing does NOT need to be included in POS to get a "YES".)
24: Are Coca-Cola identified fountain cups available in this outlet?
25: PICOS POI - Are there a minimum 3 Monster POIs from curb to cold vault?  (Curb in POI for MONSTER, Minimum of 3 MONSTER POIs.  May include coolers, Displays, POP elements.)
26: Are all displays properly priced?
27: Are all SKU's in cold vault/equipment properly priced?

1a.  Are ANY of the following 2018 Innovation Brands available in Impulse Zone area? (Coke Origins, Diet Coke Recast, Fanta Apple, VW Active, Core Power Coffee, Fuze 16.9 oz, Powerade Blue Rasp. Cherry, New Dasani Sparkling Flavors, Hubert's Lemonade, McCafe, MM Watermelon, New Dunkin Flavors, Monster Ultra Violet, Gold Peak Unsweet Rasp, Gold Peak Slight Sweet Lemon, Honest Tea Glass, Zico Jalapeno Mango)
